where the matter to be affected is situated. The last day of publication shall be at least thirty
days prior to introduction of the bill.
Proposed House Rule provides that a notice of the intent to introduce a bill to enact a local
or special law that is caused to be published by a person other than a member of the
legislature shall include the name of the person who caused the notice to be published.
(Adds House Rule 7.20)
